msgid ""
"Open a note in a dedicated pop-out window and verify updates persist back"
" to SQLite."
msgstr "在独立弹窗中打开便签，并验证更新会正确写回 SQLite。"

#: ../../07-testing.md:27 ca7848f51c1549d38cab64cb855d9b78
msgid ""
"Confirm external Markdown links open via the shell plugin instead of "
"navigating inside the webview."
msgstr "确认外部 Markdown 链接通过 shell 插件打开，而不是在 webview 内部跳转。"

#: ../../07-testing.md:29 cd5dc6ef48d14de083ad412963b60b7c
msgid "Pomodoro"
msgstr "番茄钟"

#: ../../07-testing.md:31 9acad69c47914f29896362daccc264f1
msgid "Save timer durations and milestone settings."
msgstr "保存计时器时长和里程碑设置。"

#: ../../07-testing.md:32 074f6fab34944bf68cd3744734787c15
msgid "Start, pause, resume, skip, and reset a cycle."
msgstr "测试一个周期的开始、暂停、继续、跳过和重置。"

#: ../../07-testing.md:33 6f848efa88064658b3c00d69a7b08054
msgid "Verify the tray tooltip changes during active sessions."
msgstr "验证活动会话期间托盘提示文字会变化。"

#: ../../07-testing.md:34 8109137498fe46b9aad06ee49ca70c7b
msgid ""
"Confirm milestone status updates between `active`, `completed`, and "
"`cancelled`."
msgstr "确认里程碑状态能够在 `active`、`completed` 和 `cancelled` 之间正确切换。"

#: ../../07-testing.md:36 cad547ad008d491ea30a19d46556115e
msgid "Settings and Storage"
msgstr "设置与存储"

#: ../../07-testing.md:38 bc4d6b396f794d63b5f4e3c4250c6567
msgid ""
"Update page size, todo display, note display, note folder, and note "
"template."
msgstr "更新 page size、todo display、note display、note folder 和 note template。"

#: ../../07-testing.md:39 756088fdebfb430ea06382153ae89abf
msgid "Restart the app and confirm settings reload from `app_settings`."
msgstr "重启应用，确认设置会从 `app_settings` 中重新加载。"

#: ../../07-testing.md:40 b3309846bcc0474aa30e207a72ca0ac1
msgid ""
"Verify database directory precedence: `LAZY_TODO_DB_DIR`, config file, "
"then app data dir."
msgstr "验证数据库目录优先级：`LAZY_TODO_DB_DIR`、配置文件、最后是应用数据目录。"

#: ../../07-testing.md:42 eb665944c2af4727b52d67e164f0d042
msgid "Documentation Verification"
msgstr "文档验证"

#: ../../07-testing.md:52 2901b8b49f5d40678ba23d808b3492af
msgid ""
"The English source should build to `_build/en/html/`, the Chinese site "
"should build to `_build/zh_CN/html/`, and the language switcher should be"
" present on every page."
msgstr ""
"英文源文档应构建到 `_build/en/html/`，中文站点应构建到 `_build/zh_CN/html/`，"
"并且每个页面都应显示语言切换器。"

